OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCharity shop moves online  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fas shoplifting spikes      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Charity shops say they are having to   
OL,6, get rid of changing rooms and sell     
OL,7, items online as they lose thousands of 
OL,8, pounds to a rise in shoplifting.       
OL,10,FFigures show shoplifting in Wales is at
OL,11,Fits highest level in more than 20      
OL,12,Fyears.                                 
OL,14,FThere was a 36% increase recorded by   
OL,15,Fpolice forces in Wales from September  
OL,16,F2022 to September 2023, compared with a
OL,17,F32% rise in England, ONS data showed.  
OL,19,FOne former shoplifter said sentences   
OL,20,Fgiven were not enough of a deterrent.  
